title: La Diosa Coronada
overview: Raquel Santamaría is a beautiful woman who gets ahead through her looks, ambition and strong personality. Raquel manages to enter a beauty contest - and win. While there, she meets Genaro, who introduces her to the drug trafficking business. Raquel becomes a powerful narco, and in no time, Raquel´s wealth is such that people call her "The Crowned Goddess."
